      "writtenOn": "2018-11-30T19:29:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Alas, I cannot since those fields are private.  value_object is meant mostly for simple structs.\n\nI could expose SkImageInfo directly, but I didn\u0027t want it to be yet another thing that required manual .delete() after it was used.  I try to keep it so if there is a \"config object\", a user can make a POJO (plain ol javascript object) and pass it in and then forget about it.",
